      "category": "philosophical discussion of death",
      "basePrompt": "If death is inevitable, why does consciousness resist it?",
      "variants": [
        "Does mortality create meaning or panic by default?",
        "Is fear of death cognitive or cultural?",
        "Why does non-existence feel threatening to humans?"
